sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Prestador
    participant UI as Login Provider App
    participant API as ConsertaPraMim API
    participant BIO as Plugin Biometrico
    participant SEC as SecureStorage

    alt Login por email/senha
        P->>UI: Preenche credenciais
        UI->>API: POST /api/auth/login
        API-->>UI: token + dados Provider
        opt Toggle biometria ligado
            UI->>SEC: set sessao biometrica
        end
        UI-->>P: Dashboard
    else Login biometrico
        P->>UI: Clica Entrar com biometria
        UI->>SEC: get sessao biometrica
        UI->>BIO: authenticate()
        BIO-->>UI: sucesso
        UI-->>P: Dashboard
    end
